  "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"willcl-ark\" data-post=\"17\" data-topic=\"2253\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/user_avatar/delvingbitcoin.org/willcl-ark/48/165_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> willcl-ark:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Re-reading <a href=\"https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/29912\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">bitcoin Issue#29912</a> where <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/rodarmor\">@rodarmor</a> had fleshed out a rough approach to describe the RPC api, I tweaked the approach a little bit in <a href=\"https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/compare/master...willcl-ark:bitcoin:json-rpc-schema\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">this branch</a> to generate an <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/willcl-ark/bitcoin/8eb8112c66d5d79158394ba3f6677473c57f7d87/doc/openrpc.json\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">openrpc spec file</a>, which I was able to trivially give to a chatbot to develop a dynamic webkit-based \u201cRPC GUI\u201d, based off the formal spec, in about 20 minutes.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Using this openrpc spec I (with some help from claude) have created a basic  <a href=\"https://github.com/janb84/bitcoin-tui\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">bitcoin-tui</a>  for some experimentation with what is possible with just calling the RPC.\nQuite promising !</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/3/3d7542fcd8c5c65f36451312754149a5260e8508.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/3d7542fcd8c5c65f36451312754149a5260e8508\" title=\"Bitcoin TUI\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/3/3d7542fcd8c5c65f36451312754149a5260e8508_2_690x412.jpeg\" alt=\"Bitcoin TUI\" data-base62-sha1=\"8LGmaSjq8r3SCms5rvgjtQ3t71C\" width=\"690\" height=\"412\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/3/3d7542fcd8c5c65f36451312754149a5260e8508_2_690x412.jpeg, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/3/3d7542fcd8c5c65f36451312754149a5260e8508_2_1035x618.jpeg 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/3/3d7542fcd8c5c65f36451312754149a5260e8508_2_1380x824.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"101211\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Bitcoin TUI</span><span class=\"informations\">1920\u00d71149 232 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
